  "description": {
    "canonical": "In moments of despair, let the battle resonate with song. Cantare's blades lodge into the battlefield and return upon reload. When returning blades strike enemies, Cantare empowers allies with increased Reload Speed.\r\n\r\nExperience the true power of Jade's Ensemble when Evensong, Cantare, and Harmony sing together.",
    "display": "在绝望的时刻，让歌声响彻战场。歌颂的刃片会扎入战场中，并在重新装填时返回。当返回的刃片击中敌人时，歌颂会增强友军的装填速度。\r\n\r\n当晚祷、歌颂与和谐一同奏响时，体验 Jade 之合奏真正的力量。",
    "localizationStatus": "official-zh"
  },
